{
  "stem": "20088.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she put the with the fire and she was going to cut it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And when we cut it we saw that it was a womb and it was a little horse in it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the Russians had choked it because it was pregnant and they couldn't take it along.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we still cut a bit of it and made a stew and ate it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, when I think about that, that I did this, I just think that can't be true.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I know it is true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, I mean, we did have food already, but, as I say, there was just-- we just had to eat all the time, whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So after a time we said, look, we don't know what will happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It can go on for long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We have to really decide what we were going to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We're going to go and look for-- we knew Auschwitz was not very far, the main camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let's go to Auschwitz and see if we can find the men, because we had-- the Russian had said they go on to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that night when we were sleeping, we heard a knock on the door and we didn't know who was coming.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But eventually we opened up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a-- a German, a Nazi, who was escaping, was running away from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russians was there after him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said first he is a soldier and, you know, he lost his battalion and so, and could we keep him there the night?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And give him some food?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He has been running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't dare to say no, because, you know, he was armed and we didn't want him there either.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this Polish woman said, oh, I wouldn't stay here.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
